title: Viral lockdown message has nothing to do with WHO
description: A message that is going viral on WhatsApp claims that the World Health Organisation has procedure and protocol for lockdown and that India is only in the second phase as of now.
content:
CLAIM
A message that is going viral on WhatsApp claims that the World Health Organisation (WHO) has a 'procedure and protocol' for lockdown and that India is only in the second phase of it as of now.
